                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I saw the prisoner on the night of the 9th of February - I took him into custody- I went back to the prosecutor's shop, and took these shovels.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310217-149-person1513">
                  JAMES 
                  HAYWARD
               <interp inst="t18310217-149-person1513" type="surname" value="HAYWARD"></interp>
