                  </persName>
            . These are my shovels - they had been in the street; they are generally chained, but were not then.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written Defence, stating that the witness was mistaken in his person. He received a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 19.</p>
